Item.SQL: With global_sync As (Select t1.task_id, g.global_value As task_global, eg.global_value As env_global From task_globals g, tdm_env_globals eg, tasks t1 Where t1.task_id = g.task_id And t1.environment_id = eg.environment_id And g.global_name = 'TDM_SET_SYNC_OFF' And eg.global_name = 'TDM_SET_SYNC_OFF') Select Distinct te.task_execution_id, t.task_id, t.selection_method, t.load_entity, t.delete_before_load, t.task_type, t.task_title As task_name, t.source_env_name As source_env, e.environment_name As target_env, b.be_name, Case When t.refresh_reference_data = False Then 'false' Else 'true' End As refresh_reference_data, Case When t.replace_sequences = False Then 'false' Else 'true' End As replace_sequences, t.scheduler, t.task_created_by, Case When t.version_ind = False Then 'false' Else 'true' End As version_ind, t.selected_version_task_name, t.selected_version_datetime, t.selected_ref_version_task_name, t.selected_ref_version_datetime, t.retention_period_type, t.retention_period_value, Case When t.request_of_fresh_data = False Then 'false' Else 'true' End As request_of_fresh_data, t.scheduling_end_date, Case When t.load_entity = True And t.delete_before_load = False Then 'Insert entity without delete' When t.load_entity = True And t.delete_before_load = True Then 'Delete and load entity' When t.load_entity = False And t.delete_before_load = True Then 'Delete entity without load' Else 'Extract Task' End As operation_mode, Case When global_sync.task_global Is Not Null Then global_sync.task_global When global_sync.env_global Is Not Null Then global_sync.env_global Else 'false' End As TDM_SET_SYNC_OFF From tasks t, task_execution_list te, environments e, business_entities b, tasks t1 Full Outer Join global_sync On t1.task_id = global_sync.task_id Where t.task_id = te.task_id And e.environment_id = t.environment_id And b.be_id = t.be_id And t.task_id = t1.task_id Order By te.task_execution_id
